WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
What's up, guys?

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:02.000
This is the second episode of the series,

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.000
and I've prepared an extra episode for you to enjoy.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:05.000
If you're interested,

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.000
please subscribe to my channel and like this video.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:09.000
And if you want to see more of my work,

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:11.000
check out the description below.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Thanks for watching.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:14.000
Gotoh's sitting down.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Thanks to him,

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.000
I get to watch some S-Ranks in action, though.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Well...

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:26.000
Let's kick this thing off!

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:33.000
Subtitles by the Amara.org community

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:03.000
Subtitles by the Amara.org community

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:33.000
Subtitles by the Amara.org community

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:03.000
Subtitles by the Amara.org community

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:07.000
Testing our brute strength?

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:08.000
Yeah!

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:09.000
Nice and simple!

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:10.000
All right.

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:13.000
You're about to see size does matter!

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:24.000
I can't beat speedsters in close combat.

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:29.000
In case you didn't know,

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:30.000
my specialty is...

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:31.000
Rage attacks!

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:35.000
Hoshino!

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:36.000
Watch where you're going!

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:37.000
Hurry and take him down!

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:43.000
Just checking,

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:45.000
but they have reinforced this place

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:47.000
with the highest quality of Essence Stone,

00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:48.000
right, Chairman Goh?

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:49.000
Yes.

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:51.000
I'm thinking we may have to re-evaluate

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:52.000
how sturdy it really is, though.

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:55.000
These guys are the cream of the crop

00:02:55.000 --> 00:02:57.000
among S-Rank hunters.

00:02:57.000 --> 00:02:59.000
We need to approach this fight

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:00.000
and make sure they're not just trying

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:01.000
to grab my wrists,

00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:02.000
but to snap them.

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:08.000
Atsushi Kumamoto...

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:09.000
Doesn't seem very aggressive

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:11.000
for a combat type.

00:03:13.000 --> 00:03:14.000
Dammit!

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:16.000
I'm not cut out for this at all...

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:18.000
I just don't have the heart for it.

00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:22.000
Is Gotoh using us,

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:23.000
seeing if his hunters are ready

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:25.000
to fight the ants?

00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:26.000
If that's the idea,

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:27.000
I'm here for it.

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:28.000
Heh.

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:31.000
I'm not going to let you get away with this.

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:32.000
I'm going to get you.

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:33.000
I'm going to get you.

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:35.000
So I'm supposed to be a test, huh?

00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:37.000
Time to see if you pass or fail!

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:38.000
Nope.

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:39.000
I'm outta here!

00:03:44.000 --> 00:03:46.000
What a bunch of maniacs.

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:47.000
A little A-Rank like me

00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:48.000
would get smoked.

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:49.000
No way!

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:50.000
You're like the fairy definition

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:51.000
of pure grit

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:52.000
and plenty tough, too!

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:56.000
In terms of physical strength,

00:03:56.000 --> 00:03:57.000
guess I win.

00:03:57.000 --> 00:03:58.000
Heh heh.

00:03:59.000 --> 00:04:00.000
Who'd have thought

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:02.000
I'd be eating the floor?

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:04.000
It's a humbling first for me.

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:07.000
I believe you lose.

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:12.000
Is running your only tactic?

00:04:15.000 --> 00:04:16.000
If you're targeting me

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:18.000
over Hunter Cha,

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:20.000
you must think I'm the weakest link.

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:24.000
I can't predict her moves.

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:25.000
She's equal parts graceful

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:26.000
and deadly.

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:27.000
Now I see why they call her

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:28.000
the Dancer.

00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:30.000
It's frighteningly accurate.

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:38.000
I'd better help Hunter back.

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:46.000
Did you see that?

00:04:46.000 --> 00:04:47.000
Oh no.

00:04:47.000 --> 00:04:49.000
My last shot on reflex.

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:55.000
Aw, hell.

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:56.000
Looks like he snapped again.

00:04:56.000 --> 00:04:57.000
Yeah.

00:04:57.000 --> 00:04:59.000
Which means all bets are off now.

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:01.000
Do you think we should intervene?

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:04.000
Not if their lives aren't in danger, no.

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:09.000
He's fast.

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:14.000
Okay, you guys,

00:05:14.000 --> 00:05:15.000
this is getting bad.

00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:23.000
Sorry to interrupt you there.

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:25.000
But this doesn't feel like

00:05:25.000 --> 00:05:26.000
a friendly sparring match.

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:27.000
The hell are you?

00:05:27.000 --> 00:05:28.000
That's crazy.

00:05:28.000 --> 00:05:29.000
He laid out Kumamoto

00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:30.000
in his berserk state.

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:31.000
You said this one is registered

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:32.000
as a mage type?

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:33.000
Yes, sir.

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:34.000
That's what I heard, at least.

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:35.000
Might have to confirm that myself.

00:05:35.000 --> 00:05:36.000
Hunter Cha,

00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:37.000
are you good to accept

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:38.000
the loss for this match?

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:39.000
Since Hunter Beck seems

00:05:39.000 --> 00:05:40.000
to have tapped out as well.

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:41.000
Sure.

00:05:41.000 --> 00:05:42.000
Even if I'd gone all out,

00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:43.000
the result would be

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:44.000
that I'd lost.

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:45.000
Oh, I see.

00:05:45.000 --> 00:05:46.000
So I'm going to have to

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:47.000
do what you're doing.

00:05:47.000 --> 00:05:48.000
I'm going to have to

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:49.000
make sure that this match

00:05:49.000 --> 00:05:50.000
is a good one.

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:51.000
Yeah, that's right.

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:52.000
I'm going to have to

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:53.000
make sure that this match

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:54.000
is a good one.

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:55.000
Even if I'd gone all out,

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:56.000
the result would have been

00:05:56.000 --> 00:05:57.000
the same.

00:05:59.000 --> 00:06:00.000
Hunter Sung,

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:02.000
if you're up for a round,

00:06:02.000 --> 00:06:03.000
Guildmaster Gotoh

00:06:03.000 --> 00:06:04.000
would like to challenge you.

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:07.000
He's looking for a fight.

00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:09.000
Don't need a translation

00:06:09.000 --> 00:06:10.000
to know that.

00:06:11.000 --> 00:06:12.000
Good.

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:13.000
I've been wanting to try out

00:06:13.000 --> 00:06:14.000
the skills I got

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:15.000
from the Demon's Castle.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:18.000
Is the thought of facing me funny?

00:06:19.000 --> 00:06:20.000
Gotoh-san,

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:21.000
good news.

00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:22.000
Hunter Sung has agreed

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:23.000
to spar with you.

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:24.000
On one condition.

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:25.000
However.

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:26.000
What's that?

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:27.000
He'll only fight

00:06:27.000 --> 00:06:28.000
if you don't hold back

00:06:28.000 --> 00:06:29.000
on him, sir.

00:06:32.000 --> 00:06:33.000
Fine by me.

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:35.000
The Jeju Island raid

00:06:35.000 --> 00:06:36.000
draws closer

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:38.000
and all eyes are on the Hunters.

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:39.000
The world is waiting to see

00:06:39.000 --> 00:06:40.000
if this alliance with Japan

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:41.000
will be enough

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:42.000
to tip the scales of victory

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:43.000
in our favor.

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:44.000
Jiihi, don't you got work?

00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:45.000
I'm off.

00:06:45.000 --> 00:06:46.000
Told you yesterday.

00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:48.000
Really?

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:50.000
Well, don't slack too much.

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:51.000
Gotta do our best,

00:06:51.000 --> 00:06:52.000
just like the Hunters

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:53.000
out there are doing.

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:54.000
Hello.

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:55.000
Um...

00:06:55.000 --> 00:06:56.000
I have questions

00:06:56.000 --> 00:06:57.000
about the Jeju Raid's defense

00:06:57.000 --> 00:06:58.000
if you have time.

00:06:58.000 --> 00:06:59.000
What's happening now?

00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:00.000
Guess our renowned

00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:01.000
10th S-Rank

00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:02.000
is feeling feisty.

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:03.000
He's fixing to go

00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:04.000
head to head

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:05.000
with Gotoh.

00:07:05.000 --> 00:07:06.000
He held his own

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:07.000
in that A-Rank dungeon,

00:07:07.000 --> 00:07:08.000
but I wonder

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:09.000
how he'll do

00:07:09.000 --> 00:07:10.000
against the Red-Hat.

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:11.000
That's what he'll do

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:12.000
if he has a chance

00:07:12.000 --> 00:07:13.000
to get out of here.

00:07:13.000 --> 00:07:14.000
He's doing as he's

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:15.000
supposed to do,

00:07:15.000 --> 00:07:16.000
but,

00:07:16.000 --> 00:07:17.000
I mean,

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:18.000
I don't know

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:19.000
what he'll do

00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:20.000
if he gets out

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:21.000
and it's too late.

00:07:21.000 --> 00:07:22.000
I think,

00:07:22.000 --> 00:07:24.560
I wonder how he'll do against an S-rank Hunter.

00:07:24.560 --> 00:07:26.680
Surprised you don't have your handkerchief.

00:07:26.680 --> 00:07:28.839
The smell of Hunter's not bothering you?

00:07:28.839 --> 00:07:33.139
It's not like I can keep my nose covered while I'm on the battlefield.

00:07:33.139 --> 00:07:35.579
Should we stop this before it starts?

00:07:35.579 --> 00:07:39.259
The spellcaster going up against a melee hunter in close combat.

00:07:39.259 --> 00:07:41.759
Normally I'd say it's a bad idea,

00:07:41.759 --> 00:07:45.360
but I bet I'm thinking the same thing you are about this matchup.

00:07:45.360 --> 00:07:49.220
And I'm sure my hopes are just as high.

00:07:49.220 --> 00:07:54.220
Because if I'm right, Hunter's sung has a rare ability to keep growing stronger.

00:07:56.620 --> 00:07:57.620
Okay, let's...

00:08:02.160 --> 00:08:04.640
Come on, man. Not cool.

00:08:04.640 --> 00:08:06.640
He's awfully nimble.

00:08:06.640 --> 00:08:08.700
And people think he's a mage.

00:08:08.700 --> 00:08:09.700
What a joke.

00:08:12.680 --> 00:08:15.280
I'll expose you for what you really are.

00:08:16.620 --> 00:08:17.420
Oh yeah.

00:08:17.420 --> 00:08:19.220
He's definitely a step above the others.

00:08:19.220 --> 00:08:22.220
But I can still dodge him.

00:08:22.220 --> 00:08:24.220
Smiling again?

00:08:24.220 --> 00:08:26.620
I'm going cross-eyed trying to keep up.

00:08:26.620 --> 00:08:29.000
He's really hanging in there, isn't he?

00:08:29.000 --> 00:08:32.160
Evading such quick attacks is very impressive.

00:08:32.160 --> 00:08:34.800
It's not that he's hanging in there, though.

00:08:34.800 --> 00:08:37.480
He's egging him on to test his strength.

00:08:41.980 --> 00:08:44.920
This whole runaround thing is getting on my nerves.

00:08:44.920 --> 00:08:46.620
Change of plans.

00:08:46.620 --> 00:08:48.660
I'm gonna kill him!

00:08:48.659 --> 00:08:49.659
I'm gonna kill him!

00:08:56.659 --> 00:08:57.659
Is he alright?

00:09:03.159 --> 00:09:06.159
Careful with that thing. Someone could've lost an eye.

00:09:06.159 --> 00:09:08.659
Is he toying with me by grabbing my hand?

00:09:08.659 --> 00:09:12.659
I can only guess what you just said.

00:09:12.659 --> 00:09:16.059
But grabbing your wrist would end the game.

00:09:16.059 --> 00:09:18.100
And neither of us want it to be over so soon.

00:09:18.100 --> 00:09:18.620
So...

00:09:18.659 --> 00:09:20.559
and only make ends meet.

00:09:20.559 --> 00:09:22.259
Maybe we'll win.

00:09:31.259 --> 00:09:31.699
Deer!

00:09:31.699 --> 00:09:32.699
Nóircul!

00:09:32.699 --> 00:09:34.159
Explosions do not work!

00:09:34.159 --> 00:09:36.039
We have to

00:09:36.039 --> 00:09:37.000
find something.

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:38.059
That dolce

00:09:38.059 --> 00:09:38.699
trust

00:09:38.699 --> 00:09:41.659
I won't be lost!

00:09:44.360 --> 00:09:45.259
What the-

00:09:46.699 --> 00:09:47.139
Hunter Sung! That's enough!

00:09:47.139 --> 00:09:47.919
Mal upright!

00:09:47.919 --> 00:09:48.519
All good!

00:09:48.659 --> 00:09:53.240
Son, this fight's getting out of hand. Let's call it here, while you're both in one piece.

00:09:53.899 --> 00:09:55.919
Tell your guildmaster this match is over.

00:09:56.299 --> 00:09:57.339
Oh, right.

00:10:00.059 --> 00:10:01.759
Did I spoil your fun?

00:10:02.240 --> 00:10:02.659
No.

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:08.799
You fought the great Ryuji Goto and lived. All he managed to do was nick you once. Good on ya.

00:10:10.919 --> 00:10:17.939
I got a little more intense than I meant to, but I have a good grasp of everyone's skills now.

00:10:17.940 --> 00:10:20.960
You sent soldiers into five of their shadows, too.

00:10:24.140 --> 00:10:28.340
Thank you. Later I'll send you the list of hunters participating in the raid.

00:10:29.060 --> 00:10:31.800
And forward it to our vice guildmaster, too, please.

00:10:32.060 --> 00:10:32.680
Take care.

00:10:38.020 --> 00:10:38.860
Chairman Goh.

00:10:40.360 --> 00:10:42.580
Ah, Hunter Sung. How can I help you?

00:10:43.160 --> 00:10:44.940
So, about this Jeju Island raid...

00:10:47.940 --> 00:10:50.480
I'm afraid you're not even ready to talk about this, huh?

00:10:51.960 --> 00:10:54.660
Regi. You'd be shocked by how good one of these hunters is.

00:10:56.280 --> 00:10:59.400
I doubt he compares to the guildmaster of the Drawn Sword.

00:10:59.400 --> 00:11:00.540
Don't be so sure.

00:11:00.540 --> 00:11:01.540
Which one is it?

00:11:01.540 --> 00:11:06.140
Sung. Jinoo. He's the recently reawakened S-Rank.

00:11:06.140 --> 00:11:10.680
Hmm. Okay, that's strange. I have the list for the raid here.

00:11:10.680 --> 00:11:12.440
But his name's not on it.

00:11:12.440 --> 00:11:13.700
It's not?

00:11:15.020 --> 00:11:16.140
I don't see Hunter Sung.

00:11:16.140 --> 00:11:17.720
I guess he won't be joining the raid after all.

00:11:17.720 --> 00:11:20.519
I'm sure he has his reasons. Either way...

00:11:20.519 --> 00:11:24.720
Younger's name is missing too. Either way...

00:11:24.720 --> 00:11:29.120
We've got a solid team of 15 S-Rank hunters that are pledged to our cause.

00:11:29.120 --> 00:11:31.720
This time's going to be different.

00:11:35.720 --> 00:11:37.720
This time we'll win.

00:11:40.720 --> 00:11:41.720
I'm home.

00:11:41.720 --> 00:11:43.720
Yeah, about time.

00:11:44.720 --> 00:11:46.720
Hey sweetie, dinner's ready.

00:11:46.720 --> 00:11:48.720
I'd say your timing's perfect.

00:11:49.720 --> 00:11:51.720
Let's eat then.

00:11:52.720 --> 00:11:56.720
Mom just woke up from a four year coma. She needs me.

00:11:57.720 --> 00:12:01.720
Which is why... I'm not going to Jeju Island.

00:12:05.720 --> 00:12:10.720
My subjects need food, but there is no prey.

00:12:10.720 --> 00:12:15.720
They're cannibalizing each other to sustain themselves.

00:12:15.720 --> 00:12:16.720
This way.

00:12:16.720 --> 00:12:17.720
Won't do.

00:12:17.720 --> 00:12:20.720
We must leave the island.

00:12:20.720 --> 00:12:23.720
I need stronger offspring.

00:12:23.720 --> 00:12:26.720
More powerful than any other.

00:12:26.720 --> 00:12:31.720
Capable of leading my mighty queen of...

00:12:31.720 --> 00:12:33.720
...S-Rank.

00:12:33.720 --> 00:12:35.720
...S-Rank.

00:12:35.720 --> 00:12:37.720
...S-Rank.

00:12:37.720 --> 00:12:39.720
...S-Rank.

00:12:39.720 --> 00:12:41.720
...S-Rank.

00:12:41.720 --> 00:12:43.720
...S-Rank.

00:12:43.720 --> 00:12:44.720
...S-Rank.

00:12:44.720 --> 00:12:45.720
...S-Rank.

00:12:45.720 --> 00:12:46.720
...S-Rank.

00:13:04.720 --> 00:13:06.720
Grow strong, my son...

00:13:06.720 --> 00:13:08.720
...For all of us!

00:13:08.720 --> 00:13:10.720
...For all of us!

00:13:10.720 --> 00:13:13.720
...For all of us!

00:13:13.720 --> 00:13:21.720
The ant magic beasts have been evolving at a disturbing rate. They only crawl along the ground during the first three Jeju Island raids.

00:13:21.720 --> 00:13:34.720
But as you can see in this recently captured footage, they've taken a more humanoid appearance in addition to growing large wings. In response, the Hunters Association is formulating a strategy to combat this newest threat.

00:13:38.720 --> 00:13:41.720
You messed with the wrong S-Rank, you stupid beast!

00:13:43.720 --> 00:13:46.720
This is a bad call and you know it.

00:13:46.720 --> 00:13:50.720
Every Hunter was called to join the Defense Force, so why should I?

00:13:50.720 --> 00:13:53.720
Well, Miss Han, you're an E-Rank for one thing.

00:13:53.720 --> 00:13:56.720
So that's how it's gonna be?

00:13:56.720 --> 00:13:57.720
Sorry!

00:13:58.720 --> 00:14:06.720
In the event any rogue ants make their way to the mainland, Hunters of all ranks are being enlisted as a countermeasure to protect civilians.

00:14:11.720 --> 00:14:13.720
Tonight, we race.

00:14:13.720 --> 00:14:16.720
Tomorrow, we raid Jeju Island.

00:14:20.720 --> 00:14:24.720
This is the First Fleet. We've arrived at our designated coordinates.

00:14:25.720 --> 00:14:27.720
Second Fleet here. We've arrived as well.

00:14:28.720 --> 00:14:31.720
Third Fleet has eyes on the island and is now approaching.

00:14:31.720 --> 00:14:35.720
Fourth Fleet is also en route. We anticipate arrival in five minutes.

00:14:37.720 --> 00:14:40.720
Master, do we have what it takes to beat the ants?

00:14:40.720 --> 00:14:43.720
No way of knowing for sure until we try.

00:14:43.720 --> 00:14:47.720
But we were stationed here because we're using our smarts to fight these things, too.

00:14:47.720 --> 00:14:50.720
No creepy crawly's gonna crawl past me.

00:14:50.720 --> 00:14:55.720
You're inspiring! I'll follow you for the rest of my life, however long that might be!

00:14:57.720 --> 00:15:00.720
Take care of things here, Vice Guildmaster.

00:15:00.720 --> 00:15:04.720
I'm planning to just space out. I mean, we'll be on standby.

00:15:04.720 --> 00:15:09.720
Anything can happen. Besides, knowing you're on duty puts me at ease.

00:15:09.720 --> 00:15:12.720
I can go into battle with a clear head.

00:15:14.720 --> 00:15:16.720
Please be careful, sir.

00:15:16.720 --> 00:15:17.720
Will do.

00:15:17.720 --> 00:15:20.720
What? Why the hell is Min-sung stationed up here?

00:15:20.720 --> 00:15:23.720
Do you know how much he's worth? I can't have him getting eaten by ants.

00:15:23.720 --> 00:15:25.720
Tell him to hide in the back!

00:15:39.720 --> 00:15:41.720
I'll get him out of here.

00:15:41.720 --> 00:15:42.720
I'll be right back.

00:15:42.720 --> 00:15:49.720
All squads have made contact. The Mainland Force, the Coastal Guard, and the team on Jeju.

00:15:49.720 --> 00:15:52.720
The diversionary unit has landed on the island as well.

00:15:55.720 --> 00:16:00.720
A heartening turnout. So many hunters heard the call to arms and answered without question.

00:16:00.720 --> 00:16:05.720
Including a very surprising, yet very welcome addition.

00:16:05.720 --> 00:16:07.720
I'm ready. How about you?

00:16:09.720 --> 00:16:11.720
I'm ready.

00:16:12.720 --> 00:16:13.720
Pyunggu.

00:16:14.720 --> 00:16:16.720
Could've sworn you said you were retired.

00:16:16.720 --> 00:16:21.720
Yeah, but then I realized. Without a healer, you'd be dead in a matter of seconds.

00:16:21.720 --> 00:16:24.720
You see a magic beast and charge straight in without thinking.

00:16:24.720 --> 00:16:28.720
Because if I didn't, they'd make a beeline for you and tear you to shreds.

00:16:34.720 --> 00:16:36.720
It's like a ghost town.

00:16:37.720 --> 00:16:38.720
Alpha here.

00:16:38.720 --> 00:16:39.720
All hunters sound off.

00:16:39.720 --> 00:16:41.720
Team Bravo, in position.

00:16:41.720 --> 00:16:43.720
Charlie here. In position.

00:16:43.720 --> 00:16:46.720
Team Delta, we're ready for action.

00:16:48.720 --> 00:16:50.720
A live broadcast?

00:16:50.720 --> 00:16:54.720
Yes. Well, mostly. There's a ten minute delay to edit the intense scenes.

00:16:54.720 --> 00:16:59.720
As a cameraman, it's a true honor to be documenting this historic clash for the whole world to see.

00:16:59.720 --> 00:17:04.720
Sure. When hunters have something or someone to protect, they always up their game.

00:17:04.720 --> 00:17:07.720
That said, you do know being behind that lens will be a challenge.

00:17:07.720 --> 00:17:14.720
I'll be okay, sir. Though you wouldn't guess it, I'm an A-Rank. I'm used to filming hazardous stuff.

00:17:14.720 --> 00:17:16.720
Well then, welcome aboard.

00:17:16.720 --> 00:17:22.720
This is probably the first time the public will ever see a raid like this, but it might also be the last.

00:17:22.720 --> 00:17:25.720
Hell, it had better be.

00:17:25.720 --> 00:17:28.720
Let's put a proper end to this story.

00:17:28.720 --> 00:17:33.720
If we don't pull this off, our whole country could be wiped from the map.

00:17:33.720 --> 00:17:36.720
More than ever, we need a hero.

00:17:37.720 --> 00:17:41.720
I just got word. The strike team is prepared to mobilize.

00:17:41.720 --> 00:17:47.720
All right. This is it. Let the fourth Jeju Island raid commence.

00:17:47.720 --> 00:17:49.720
Release your full strength.

00:17:49.720 --> 00:17:50.720
Roger.

00:17:51.720 --> 00:17:53.720
The diversionary unit is making its move.

00:17:53.720 --> 00:17:56.720
This bait is really something else.

00:17:56.720 --> 00:17:58.720
There go the ants.

00:17:59.720 --> 00:18:01.720
Just had to target our transport.

00:18:01.720 --> 00:18:04.720
Please open the hatch. I'll handle it.

00:18:07.720 --> 00:18:12.720
We've got some çek ziem.

00:18:12.720 --> 00:18:15.720
It was a long time ago.

00:18:15.720 --> 00:18:16.720
What was that?

00:18:16.720 --> 00:18:18.720
No one had fewicio.

00:18:18.720 --> 00:18:20.720
Well, your string will build up.

00:18:20.720 --> 00:18:22.720
You need meters of warmth to go inside this en documents.

00:18:22.720 --> 00:18:23.720
Too far!

00:18:23.720 --> 00:18:26.720
But your crane will not budge.

00:18:26.720 --> 00:18:28.720
With this tool, you can keep it moving.

00:18:28.720 --> 00:18:30.720
If you push it, Emil will be Weil Fu.

00:18:31.720 --> 00:18:34.339
It is two young men from the other side, ready to spare their lives.

00:18:34.720 --> 00:18:35.720
immني

00:18:35.720 --> 00:18:41.460
Well, hot damn! That's our ultimate weapon for you! Yes, sirree!

00:18:42.000 --> 00:18:44.759
Let's touch down, and then make our way into the cave.

00:18:47.819 --> 00:18:51.779
The Japanese hunters should be able to distract the ants for about an hour.

00:18:52.480 --> 00:18:57.680
Which means we have to get in, take down the Queen, and get out. No pressure.

00:18:59.579 --> 00:19:03.140
It's the moment of truth, everyone. Let's go!

00:19:05.720 --> 00:19:10.240
Ready the interference signal. On my mark, activate.

00:19:10.720 --> 00:19:12.220
Transmitting now, sir.

00:19:14.339 --> 00:19:18.480
Good luck having your minions detect a distress signal now, your majesty.

00:19:21.480 --> 00:19:23.940
Keep flinching, and you'll wind up dead.

00:19:27.120 --> 00:19:29.839
Why even wait around for them to execute the Queen?

00:19:30.180 --> 00:19:33.160
Wouldn't it be a lot faster if we just killed off all the ants instead?

00:19:33.579 --> 00:19:35.240
Maybe. We could.

00:19:35.720 --> 00:19:36.720
Hmm.

00:19:36.720 --> 00:19:39.539
Don't approach it like Kenzo. He's having a field day.

00:19:39.539 --> 00:19:41.539
Where there's smoke, there's fire.

00:19:41.539 --> 00:19:43.539
That, it's that Che, the Choi guy.

00:19:43.539 --> 00:19:47.539
If he and I fought, do you think I could take him?

00:19:47.539 --> 00:19:49.539
Fire versus ice. How original.

00:19:52.539 --> 00:19:55.539
The nest is secured. Let's not waste a single second they buy us.

00:19:56.539 --> 00:19:58.539
There's a lot of tunnels to choose from.

00:19:59.539 --> 00:20:02.539
The question is, which one of them is gonna lead us to the Queen?

00:20:05.720 --> 00:20:07.720
Right now, we have to find it.

00:20:07.720 --> 00:20:09.720
We're gonna have to find a way to get to the next tunnel.

00:20:10.620 --> 00:20:12.620
How about a little warning next time, Zhongying?

00:20:13.620 --> 00:20:16.620
We don't have time to search them all, and we can't divide and conquer.

00:20:17.620 --> 00:20:23.620
But if we're after the tunnel that leads the deepest underground, I believe that's the one we want.

00:20:29.620 --> 00:20:31.620
That's the last of the daily quest.

00:20:32.620 --> 00:20:34.620
Kinda eerie how no one's around today.

00:20:35.720 --> 00:20:40.960
They formed two teams of S-Ranks, and every member is strong.

00:20:41.680 --> 00:20:43.039
It should be an easy victory.

00:20:44.920 --> 00:20:46.100
Even without me.

00:20:49.980 --> 00:20:52.000
Are we sure the Queen is down here?

00:20:52.579 --> 00:20:54.400
She might have abandoned them to run.

00:20:55.100 --> 00:20:57.279
It's an island. There's nowhere she could go.

